---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Craftbook" description="About the Craftbook blog">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Craftbook</h1>
  
  <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
    <p>
      Craftbook is a collection of ideas, notes, and tutorials on various topics. 
      The blog uses Astro, a modern static site generator, and is hosted on Cloudflare Pages.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Written in Markdown for easy content creation</li>
      <li>Supports mathematical equations using KaTeX</li>
      <li>Fast and efficient static site generation</li>
      <li>Custom domain: craftbook.thermocraft.space</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Framework:</strong> Astro</li>
      <li><strong>Styling:</strong> Tailwind CSS</li>
      <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Cloudflare Pages</li>
      <li><strong>Development:</strong> TypeScript, Docker</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>